Class FntParserBaseListener

java.lang.Object
de.s42.mq.fonts.fnt.parser.FntParserBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
FntParserListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
FntLoader
public class FntParserBaseListener
extends Object
implements FntParserListener
This class provides an empty implementation of FntParserListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
